# Meeting Notes Format

## File Naming
- Recurring meetings: `YYYY-MM-DD.md`
- Dated events with topic: `YYYY-MM-DD - Topic.md`
- All meeting notes live under `**/meetings/` folders

## Note Structure

```markdown
# YYYY-MM-DD
#work/{folder-path}

## Meeting Summary
- Key point 1
- Key point 2

## Key Discussion Points
### Topic Name
- Details and context

## Action Items
- [ ] Task description @Owner 📅 YYYY-MM-DD ([source](path/to/note.md))

## Follow-Up
- Follow-up item 1
```

## 1-on-1 Meetings

Each 1-on-1 series has its own folder: `1-on-1-{name}/`
The folder contains a `Summary.md` — an incremental summary maintained across meetings.
`Summary.md` has a `## Summarized Meetings` ledger tracking which notes have been processed.
